[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "戻りましたわ。\n二人とも、レッスンの調子はいかがかしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00098",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "社長殿！　おかえりなさいませ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00099",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "……後ろの二人は誰？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00100",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "紹介しますわ。街で声をかけたイザナとレスナですわ。\nこの後、二人のレッスンを見学しますの",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00101",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "二人も挨拶を。せっかくですから、\n練習したキャッチコピーでお願いいたしますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00102",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "？？？",
		"romanized_name": "???",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "承知！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00103",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "コンコン！　貴殿の心にお邪魔しまする！\nキツネの鬼門でございます！　以後、よしなに！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00104",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "絶対一番、ナンバーワン！　ハムスターのヨハナよ。\nネズミじゃないから、覚えておいて。よろしく",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00105",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "わぁっ……お二人とも、すごくかわいい……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00106",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "鬼門とヨハナだね！　よろしくね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00107",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "さあ、レッスンを再開しますわよ。イザナたちに\nあなたがたの素晴らしさを見せてくださいな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00108",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ワン、ツー、ワン、ツー",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00109",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "最後、決めて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00110",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "承知！　はっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00111",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "わぁ～っ！　すごいすごい！　すごいですっ！\n今のはいったいなんですか！？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00112",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "忍術よ。鬼門は忍術を使えるの。\nこれの他にも、たっくさんかっこいいのあるんだから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00113",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "ヨハナちゃんもとってもかっこよかったです！\nダンスも歌も、言葉にできないほどすごくて……！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00114",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ま、まぁね。これくらい当然よ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00115",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "アイドルって素晴らしいですね……！\n見ていると、心が躍ります！　元気になります！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00116",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "いかがでしたか？　二人のパフォーマンスは",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00117",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "すごくかっこよかったよ。アイドルってすごいんだね。\nレスナちゃんも、とても楽しそう",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00118",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "……アタシにも、できるかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00119",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ふふ……その顔。やはりわたくしの目に狂いは\nありませんでした",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00120",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "え……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00121",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたが今抱いている気持ち。それは、\nあなたを輝かせるとても大切なものですわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00122",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "答えましょう。あなたはできる。\n断言しますわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00123",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "……アタシ、アイドルやってみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00124",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3955217441086782382",
		"text": "アタシ！　アイドルになる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00125",
		"still_path_hash": "8711233837385589208",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ねこじゃらしよりハンマー！　イザナだよ！\n……どう？　似合ってるかな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00126",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "レスナ",
		"romanized_name": "Resna",
		"model_path_hash": "609796561237155831",
		"text": "かわいいよイザナちゃん！\nすっごく似合ってる！　かわいいよ！　世界一だよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_001_504_00127",
		"still_path_hash": "6580594669171159823",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "社長、いつの間に衣装用意してたのよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00128",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "あなたたちの衣装と一緒に製作していましたの。\nサイズもぴったり",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00129",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "これで、メンバーは揃いましたわ！\nこれからあなたたちは、運命共同体……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00130",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "ユニット名を発表しますわ！\nあなたたちのユニット名は――",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00131",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ララ",
		"romanized_name": "Lara",
		"model_path_hash": "4015600840793749786",
		"text": "『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』ですわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_005_504_00132",
		"still_path_hash": "803162819272915998",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "「ララ・プロダクション」所属のアイドル。\n新しいことが大好きな、しっかり者",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "「ララ・プロダクション」所属のアイドル。\nかっこよくクールに振る舞う努力家",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]